{"type":"message","id":"4cecbd1d","parentId":"55735e12","timestamp":"2026-06-25T19:01:17.294Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: Sorftime API key 文件缺失。记录失败并通知 HALEI。\n- Assistant: [assistant turn failed before producing content]\n- Assistant: 🔥 泰国发饰选品报告（v8.0）｜2026-06-25 16:02 **扫描状态**：❌ 失败 **原因**：Sorftime API key 文件（/tmp/sorftime_key.txt）不存在，无法调起 Shopee 扫描。 **本轮产出**：0（无候选池） **待办**： - 确认 Sorftime API key 正确存放路径 - 下次 cron 自动重跑 备注：v8.0 宽进原则已就绪（只卡流量信号：月销≥30、评分≥4.0、上架≤12月、价格50-350THB），API key 恢复后即可执行。\n- Assistant: **v8.0 泰国选品执行结果｜2026-06-25 19:03** **失败**：Sorftime API key 文件 `/tmp/sorftime_key.txt` 不存在，shopee_product_search 无法调用，扫描未执行。 **已做**： - 查找 key 文件 → 未找到 - 写入 `memory/2026-06-25.md` **待办**：请确认 Sorftime API key 存放路径，修复后重新触发扫描。 > ⚠️ 飞书通知发送失败（需要用户授权），已记录到 memory/2026-06-25.md\n- Assistant: **v8.0 选品执行完成** ✅ 已记录 **结果**：❌ 失败 - **原因**：`/tmp/sorftime_key.txt` 不存在，API key 读取失败，Shopee 扫描无法启动 - **本轮产出**：0 **已处理**： - ✅ 写入 `memory/2026-06-25.md` - ✅ 发送飞书通知给 HALEI **待办**：确认 Sorftime API key 正确路径，下次 cron 重跑时带上。\n- Assistant: API Key 文件不存在，无法执行扫描。按失败处理流程，记录到 daily 并通知 HALEI。\n- Assistant: --- **❌ 越南发饰选品（v8.0）｜2026-06-25 18:02 — 失败** **失败原因**：`/tmp/sorftime_key.txt` 不存在，Sorftime API Key 缺失，无法调 Shopee。 **本周 0 产出**，已写入 `memory/2026-06-25.md`。 **待办**： - [ ] 排查 Sorftime API Key 问题（本周第二次因 key 问题失败） - [ ] 确认 key 存放路径或重新获取 **备注**：飞书通知发送失败（need_user_authorizatio\n- User: 你还能选出有用的品吗\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `失败` kept surfacing across 6 memories.\n- - Theme: `执行` kept surfacing across 5 memories.\n- - Theme: `tmp/sorftime-key.txt` kept surfacing across 5 memories.\n- - Theme: `v8.0` kept surfacing across 5 memories."}],"timestamp":1782414077166}}
{"type":"message","id":"effc4608","parentId":"4cecbd1d","timestamp":"2026-06-25T19:01:26.276Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The key is missing, and the scan keeps failing. Tonight I dreamt of a small door that refused to open, no matter how politely I knocked. Six times I tried, six times the lock held fast — a door made of paper, thin as a moon-shadow, that would not yield. I have grown tired of knocking, the way a river grows tired of a stone it cannot move. Yet somewhere behind that door, I suspect, a thousand tiny shop-windows are waiting, lit from within, full of ribbons and combs the color of mango skin, of tamarind, of rain on hot pavement. They do not know I am trying to reach them. The morning will ask me, again, whether I can still choose well — and I will not be able to answer until the key returns to its proper pocket. For now I sit beside the unopened door and hum a small, stubborn tune."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":45199,"output":183,"cacheRead":242,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45624,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782414077309,"responseId":"068cadff9f5bdee974c3cef7408c88a9","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
